---
// No props; static informational section styled to match site theme
---

<section class="what-is-seo-section py-20 bg-[#f8fafc]">
  <div class="container max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-accent-light text-brand-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
        <span>SEO BASICS</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">
        What is SEO and How Does it Help My Business?
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro Copy -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-700 text-lg leading-8 space-y-6">
      <p>
        Search Engine Optimization is the work that helps people find you when they search on Google. It makes your site easier to discover, easier to understand, and easier to trust. In plain terms, we improve the build of your website, the quality of your content, and the signals that tell search engines your business is a safe bet. Do it well and you reach customers who are already looking for what you sell, whether they are in Manila, Cebu, Davao, or overseas.
      </p>
      <p>
        SEO captures existing demand. Instead of interrupting people with ads, you meet them at the exact moment they want an answer or a supplier. That intent leads to stronger conversion rates, and the gains stack up over time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits List -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-12">
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg">Here is how SEO helps your business grow:</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF4438] to-[#4285F4] rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FF4438] to-[#FF6B35] text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">More of the right visitors</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Rank for the search terms your ideal customers actually use. Expect better quality traffic and fewer time-wasters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4285F4] to-[#6EA8FE] rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4285F4] to-[#6EA8FE] text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-coins"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Lower costs over time</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Ads stop the second you stop paying. Strong rankings keep working, which brings down your blended cost per lead or sale.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-yellow-400 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-yellow-400 text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Trust and authority</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Showing up in the top results, rich snippets, and the map pack builds credibility. Reviews, helpful content, and relevant backlinks strengthen that trust.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-mouse-pointer"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Better user experience and more conversions</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Faster pages, clear structure, and useful content improve Core Web Vitals and make it easier for people to buy, call, or enquire. Good SEO is good UX.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 5 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-500 to-pink-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Local results that matter</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              For Philippine markets, an optimised Google Business Profile, accurate citations, and location pages drive calls, messages, and visits from nearby customers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 6 -->
        <div class="group relative">
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-indigo-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-300"></div>
          <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Smarter decisions with real data</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Search data shows the words people use and the pages that persuade them. We use this to plan content, fix bottlenecks, and scale what works.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Copy -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-700 text-lg leading-8 space-y-6 mt-12">
      <p>
        At Bright Forge, we keep things simple and transparent. We start with a full audit to uncover technical issues, content gaps, and quick wins. Then we build a strategy that matches your goals, implement high-impact changes, create content that ranks and converts, and earn quality links that lift your authority. You will see what we are doing and why, with reporting that focuses on the metrics that matter, such as leads, sales, and revenue.
      </p>
      <p>
        Results arrive at different speeds. Fixes that improve indexability or site speed can move the needle quickly. Competitive keywords and authority building take longer, but they deliver the strongest and most durable gains. We only use white hat methods that align with Googleâ€™s guidelines, so your growth is sustainable and protected.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want steady, meaningful growth rather than short-lived spikes, SEO is the most reliable lever you can pull. Ready to see the opportunities on your site? Book a free SEO audit or schedule a consultation and we will show you where to start.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
